OL,3,CHow World Cup players kept busy during
OL,4,Ca two-hour weather delay
OL,6,FThunderstorms and heavy rain led to
OL,7,Fthe first weather-induced delay of the
OL,8,FFifa World Cup on Monday, as France
OL,9,Fand Iraq's players had to wait for
OL,10,Fmore than two hours to return to the
OL,11,Fpitch.
OL,13,FFans, players and staff were all asked
OL,14,Fto seek shelter at halftime after
OL,15,Fthunderstorm warnings were triggered
OL,16,Fin the open-air Lincoln Financial
OL,17,FField stadium in Philadelphia.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
