OL,3,CHow World Cup players kept busy during
OL,4,Ca two-hour weather delay
OL,6,FThe game was paused at halftime, which
OL,7,Fended up being 1 hour 55 minutes
OL,8,Flonger than the scheduled 15-minute
OL,9,Fbreak.
OL,11,FA rule introduced by Fifa instructs
OL,12,Fthat a game must be paused for 30
OL,13,Fminutes if lightning is detected
OL,14,Fwithin an 8-mile radius. Each strike
OL,15,Fresets the clock.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
