OL,3,CHow World Cup players kept busy during
OL,4,Ca two-hour weather delay
OL,6,FFrance's manager, Didier Deschamps,
OL,7,Frevealed the surprising way players
OL,8,Fkept busy during the delay, telling
OL,9,Freporters after the game that they
OL,10,F"played cards" while waiting for the
OL,11,Fstorm to pass.
OL,13,FBut for some players, it wasn't all
OL,14,Ffun and games.
OL,16,FSuperstar striker Kylian Mbappe
OL,17,Fdescribed the wait as "very difficult"
OL,18,Fbecause the team has to stay "focused"
OL,19,Fand "engaged" in the locker room.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
