OL,3,CHow World Cup players kept busy during
OL,4,Ca two-hour weather delay
OL,6,FIt is the first time in at least
OL,7,Fseveral decades that a World Cup match
OL,8,Fwas delayed midgame due to weather.
OL,10,F"It's a question of safety," Deschamps
OL,11,Fsaid. "You can't fight against rain
OL,12,Fand lightning."
OL,14,F"We will stick to the local laws. We
OL,15,Fhave to adapt. These are very special
OL,16,Fcircumstances, and I do hope they will
OL,17,Fnot happen again."
OL,26,@yD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
