OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1782238703
OL,3,CHow World Cup players kept busy during
OL,4,Ca two-hour weather delay
OL,6,FIraq's coach Graham Arnold, said: "I
OL,7,Fthink it's the first time I
OL,8,Fexperienced it in football as a coach
OL,9,For a player. It obviously made it much
OL,10,Fharder for the players. I told the
OL,11,Fplayers, who is going to switch on
OL,12,Fmentally?"
OL,14,FWith France leading 1-0 at halftime,
OL,15,Fscoreboard messages directed the crowd
OL,16,Fat the stadium to take shelter in its
OL,17,Fcovered areas, warning that a severe
OL,18,Fstorm was on the way.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
