OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1782238703
OL,3,CHow World Cup players kept busy during
OL,4,Ca two-hour weather delay
OL,6,FThe stoppage was initially expected to
OL,7,Fextend the halftime break by 15
OL,8,Fminutes. As the delay dragged on,
OL,9,Fstadium officials announced that "the
OL,10,Fgame will resume when deemed safe".
OL,12,FThe teams returned to the field to
OL,13,Fwarm up after about 1 hour and 40
OL,14,Fminutes, prompting cheers from the
OL,15,Fcrowd.
OL,17,FCrews used squeegees to push standing
OL,18,Fwater toward the sideline of the
OL,19,Fpitch. Despite the delay, France went
OL,20,Fon to beat Iraq 3-0 on Monday and
OL,21,Fadvance to the knockout stage.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
